lead_paragraph: Few presidents of Mexico have managed to unite the country in the way Donald Trump did after he launched his U.S. presidential bid last week with a string of broadsides against America's southern neighbor.

headline.main: Mexicans Bash Trump Pinata, Call Him Imbecile
